org.greatage.ioc
Class IOCModule

java.lang.Object
  org.greatage.ioc.IOCModule

public class IOCModule
extends java.lang.Object

This class represents base module for Great Age IoC container that configures all needed core services. This are ProxyFactory, LoggerSource, ScopeManager, SymbolSource, SymbolProvider, ResourceLocator, MessagesSource, ClassAccessSource.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Ivan Khalopik
